william :privacy-class of privacy
1)intrusion upon plaintiff's seclusion or solitute,or into his private affairs
2)public disclosure of embarrassing private facts about the plaintiff
3)publicity which places the plaintiff in a false light in the public eye
4)appropriation,for the defendant's advantage, of the plaintiff's name or likeness.
1) 侵入原告隐居||独处之处||侵入其私人事务
2）公开披露原告的令人难堪的斯密信息
3) 进行使原告被公众误解的宣传
4）为被告之利益而盗用原告的姓名||销项



普通法系中的一般侵权行类型
I.negligence 过失侵权
  general neligence 一般过失侵权
  special forms of neligence 特殊过失侵权
  medical malpractice 医疗过失
  breach of statutory duty 违反成文法义务
  liability of public and statutory bodies 公共的或成文法上的主体责任
  liability of occupiers and builders 占有人与建设单位责任
  road-traffic accidents  道路交通事故

II.intentional torts 故意侵权
   interference with the person 人身侵权
   battery 殴打
   assault 恐吓
   false imprisonment 错误关押
   malicious prosecution 诬告
   abuse of process 滥用程序
   infliction of mental distress 精神损害
   interference with property and economic interest 侵犯财产与经济利益
   trepass to chattels 侵犯动产
   conversion 侵占
   trepass to land 侵占土地
   nuisance 妨害
   deceit 欺诈
   economic torts 经济侵权

II. invasion of reputation and privacy
    defamation  诽谤
    invasion of privacy  侵害隐私


